title: Arbor Skateboards :: Sucrose Initiative ~ Daniel MacDonald
description:
Daniel MacDonald is the best dancer on the team. Whether it’s cutting rug in the club or laying it down in the streets, he chooses the Sucrose Initiative 69mm Vice on our proprietary Groovetube Cores to cha-cha down to the bottom of his neighborhood sketchball run.
The Sucrose Initiative was developed to bring rider-based design and quality material driven performance together to deliver a product that is friendly to the earth and your wallet.
Film/Edit: Alex Ameen
Check out the full line here: arborcollective.com/skateboards/products/wheels/
